abstract: >-
  Companion code and computed artifacts for Convex Core, a deterministic,
  drawdown-controlled ETF allocation framework, validated with pre-registered
  tests and published negative results. The principal directs and reviews an
  autonomous agentic-AI research pipeline; no large-language model participates
  in the allocation math. Hypothetical, backtested performance; not investment advice.
